Dialogue: 100,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你闭眼了! \N{\rENG}You blinked!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.46,0:00:06.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们再拍一张吧\N{\rENG}Let's just take another one.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.82,0:00:07.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 等下\N{\rENG}Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.72,0:00:10.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}用一个漂亮的背景合影如何? \N{\rENG}What if we get a shot with the beautiful view behind us?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.82,0:00:12.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快点, 史蒂文! \N{\rENG}Come on, Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.66,0:00:15.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说 "奶酪" \N{\rENG}Say "cheese."
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.74,0:00:17.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}奶酪! \N{\rENG}Cheese!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.58,0:00:18.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么样? \N{\rENG}Did it do it?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.94,0:00:19.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}再按一次\N{\rENG}Press it again.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我一直在按啊\N{\rENG}I've been pressing it.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.22,0:00:25.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们好可爱啊\N{\rENG}You guys look cute.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.92,0:00:26.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米! \N{\rENG}Jamie!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.18,0:00:29.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么样 史蒂文? 好久不见\N{\rENG}What's up, Steven? Long time no see.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.26,0:00:32.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...的...天! \N{\rENG}Oh...My...Gosh!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.64,0:00:34.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米, 这是康妮\N{\rENG}Jamie, this is Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你好, 康妮\N{\rENG}Greetings, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么. 你之前都在哪? \N{\rENG}So, where you been at?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 你知道的, 就是花了点时间\N{\rENG}Oh, you know, just spent some time
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.54,0:00:42.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}逛逛大制作诞生的地方\N{\rENG}where all the big pictures are made.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.36,0:00:44.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 是哪? \N{\rENG}Uh, where's that?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就是个小地方, 叫...\N{\rENG}Just a little place called...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}堪堪堪萨斯\N{\rENG}Kannnnsas.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢! 你是想当演员吗? \N{\rENG}Oh! Are you an aspiring thespian?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.90,0:00:53.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 是 的\N{\rENG}Why, a-yes, I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.64,0:00:56.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔, 我还不知道你想当演员啊\N{\rENG}Wow. I didn't know you wanted to be an actor.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.76,0:00:57.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是因为...\N{\rENG}That's because...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.54,0:01:00.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我擅长表演\N{\rENG}I'm very good at acting.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是是你戴写着 "电影明星" \N{\rENG}Is that why you're wearing those cool glasses
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.42,0:01:05.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}的炫酷眼镜的原因? \N{\rENG}that say "movie star"?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.70,0:01:07.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...其实...不是\N{\rENG}Uh...Well...No.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.90,0:01:09.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这只是从纪念品店买的\N{\rENG}I just bought these at a souvenir shop.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我怀念当个平凡邮递员的日子, \N{\rENG}I missed being a regular old mailman,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.70,0:01:12.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我回来了\N{\rENG}so I just came back.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.36,0:01:15.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且, 呃, 我走的这段时间你有收到很多邮件\N{\rENG}And, uh, you got a lot of mail while I was gone.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.44,0:01:19.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来邮政服务一直很懈怠啊\N{\rENG}Looks like the postal service has been slacking off.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.52,0:01:21.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米是唯一一个知道我住哪的邮递员\N{\rENG}Jamie's the only mailman that knows where I live.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我还需要很多的签收\N{\rENG}I'm gonna need a lot of signatures, as well.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的关节居然没声音\N{\rENG}Your knuckles are so quiet.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.88,0:01:28.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的手很讲礼节\N{\rENG}My hands are polite.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.24,0:01:30.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 石榴\N{\rENG}Oh. Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗨, 石榴! \N{\rENG}Hi, Garnet! Hello, Garnet!
Dialogue: 600,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.94,Hint,,0,0,0,,石榴出水的场景源自007系列电影"Dr.No"
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁是石--\N{\rENG}Who's gar--
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.16,0:01:41.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你好\N{\rENG}Howdy.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在干哈, 石榴? \N{\rENG}Whatcha up to, Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我刚才在海底\N{\rENG}I was just at the bottom of the ocean
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}寻找青金石和铁石英的踪迹\N{\rENG}checking for signs of Lapis and Jasper.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.26,0:01:48.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么样? \N{\rENG}Any luck?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没有\N{\rENG}Nope.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.62,0:01:53.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么可能游到海底? \N{\rENG}How were you able to swim to the bottom of the ocean?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.62,0:01:54.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很简单\N{\rENG}It was easy.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我擅长游泳\N{\rENG}I'm a really good swimmer.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打扰一下\N{\rENG}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 600,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.20,Hint,,0,0,0,,石榴去除体表水分的动作源自 "歪小子斯科特" 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.66,0:02:06.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Uh, Steven,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.32,0:02:10.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么你会收到那么多盒海人? \N{\rENG}why did you receive so many boxes of sea pals?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 我一开始只订了一盒, 但一直没收到\N{\rENG}Uh, I ordered one at first, but it never showed up.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.24,0:02:14.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我反复下单\N{\rENG}So I kept ordering.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要建个农场吗? \N{\rENG}Are you going to start a farm?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.28,0:02:17.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要放生他们\N{\rENG}I'm gonna set them free.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}回到大海! \N{\rENG}Into the sea!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.28,0:02:22.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米! \N{\rENG}Jamie!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗨, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}H-hi. Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.72,0:02:27.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不会带来了更多的的海人吧? \N{\rENG}You didn't bring more sea pals?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.12,0:02:30.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么? 不, 我只是, 呃...\N{\rENG}What? No, I just came to, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.14,0:02:33.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是什么? \N{\rENG}What's that?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 这是...呃...\N{\rENG}Uhh, it's...Uhh...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.92,0:02:37.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给你! \N{\rENG}Here!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这是...什么? \N{\rENG}But what is...It?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米! \N{\rENG}Jamie!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴! 石榴! 石榴! \N{\rENG}Garnet! Garnet! Garnet!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}最不可思议的事情发生了! \N{\rENG}The most unbelievable thing has happened!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你绝对会被吓死的! \N{\rENG}You'll absolutely die of shock!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很忙, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}I'm busy, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你收到了一封信! \N{\rENG}But you got a letter!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.24,0:03:07.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}读一下\N{\rENG}Read it.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.88,0:03:10.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}" 致石榴... "\N{\rENG}"To Garnet..."
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.74,0:03:13.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}" 当我目睹你如远古海洋仙女般站起,  "\N{\rENG}"When I saw you rise like an ancient sea nymph,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一根白热的钢筋刺穿了\N{\rENG}a white-hot steel pierced
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我身体最深处的动脉; 你\N{\rENG}the deepest artery of my being -- you.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是个心脏手术师\N{\rENG}You are a cardiac surgeon,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我是你的心脏移植患者\N{\rENG}and I am your transplant patient.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你淡定自若的站在我的胸前\N{\rENG}And you stand poised over my chest,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}握着我仍在跳动的心\N{\rENG}holding my still-beating heart,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}犹豫着, 等待着, 猜想着\N{\rENG}hesitating, waiting, wondering.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我恳求你与我共进晚餐\N{\rENG}So I implore you to join me for dinner,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者是午餐, 如果你想随意点的话\N{\rENG}or maybe lunch if you want to keep it casual,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}下周五在蟹摊\N{\rENG}next Friday at the crab shack.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.64,0:03:36.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我等待着你的回复\N{\rENG}I await your response,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就如同山茶花等待着月亮的升起\N{\rENG}as the camellia awaits the rise of the moon.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为, 你了解, 类似晚上盛开之类的\N{\rENG}'Cause, you know, it only blooms at night and stuff.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}" 爱你的, 杰米 "\N{\rENG}"Love, Jamie."
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我认为杰米要约你出去--\N{\rENG}I think Jamie is asking you out --
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}约会! \N{\rENG}on a date!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没可能\N{\rENG}Well, that ain't happening.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没戏\N{\rENG}Nope.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么? \N{\rENG}Why not?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴已经确定关系了\N{\rENG}Garnet is already in a relationship.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等, 真的? \N{\rENG}Wait, really?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 没错, 她就是个关系\N{\rENG}Well, yeah. She is a relationship.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦. 你是指, 因为她是个融合体\N{\rENG}Oh, you mean, 'cause she's a fusion.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}红宝石和蓝宝石是如此亲近\N{\rENG}Ruby and Sapphire are so close
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们无法忍受分离\N{\rENG}that they can't stand to be apart.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.16,0:04:11.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我猜与杰米的这次约会已经没有悬念了\N{\rENG}So I guess this date with Jamie is out of the question.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}三人成众\N{\rENG}Three's a crowd.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但, 伙计们, 杰米花了如此多心思\N{\rENG}But, guys, Jamie put so much thought
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.94,0:04:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}写的这封信! \N{\rENG}into this letter!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果不回复的话太粗鲁了! \N{\rENG}It would be rude not to reply!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧, 石榴\N{\rENG}Okay, Garnet,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许用他的信的口吻写最好\N{\rENG}it might be best to play off the tone of his letter
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}先用类似" 最亲爱的杰米 "开头\N{\rENG}and start off with something like, "dearest Jamie."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧, 开始吧, 石榴\N{\rENG}Okay, go for it, Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}最开始是 "不" \N{\rENG}Start with the letter "n."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧, 然后呢? \N{\rENG}Okay. What next?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃..."要"\N{\rENG}Uh...The letter "o."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 好吧\N{\rENG}Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你可以直接把单词说出来, 而不是挨个字母拼\N{\rENG}You can just say the whole word instead of spelling it out.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}句号\N{\rENG}Period.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以,  "不" "要" "." ? \N{\rENG}So, "n," "o," period?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢...\N{\rENG}Ohhh.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我认为我们得写得多点\N{\rENG}I think we'll need more than that.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"没戏, 永远\N{\rENG}"The end. Forever.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}和永远的以后"\N{\rENG}And even after that."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.96,0:04:49.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"你真诚的，石榴"\N{\rENG}"Yours truly, Garnet."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.27,0:04:50.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯...\N{\rENG}Hmm.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}至少这个很真挚并且简练\N{\rENG}At least it's honest and to the point.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你觉得他会在哪？\N{\rENG}Where do you think he could be?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他可能在派送邮件\N{\rENG}He could be dropping off mail
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}满世界转悠\N{\rENG}halfway around the world by now.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他在那！\N{\rENG}There he is!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.36,0:05:03.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米\N{\rENG}Jamie.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 嘿, 康妮和史蒂文\N{\rENG}Oh, hey, Connie and Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们来这里\N{\rENG}You guys come out here
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也是为了望着大海思考人生? \N{\rENG}to stare at the ocean and think about life, too?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...不? \N{\rENG}Uh...No?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们来这里, 呃--\N{\rENG}We came to, uh --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错, 生活如疯\N{\rENG}yeah. Life is crazy.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}前一天, 你还在沙滩市配送邮件\N{\rENG}One day, you're right here in Beach City, delivering mail,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}接着你就发现\N{\rENG}and then the next thing you know,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在前往堪萨斯的巴士上\N{\rENG}you're on a bus to Kansas
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}追寻你成为演员的梦想\N{\rENG}following your dreams of becoming an actor.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} "追寻你的梦想, " 他们说道\N{\rENG}"Follow your dreams," they said.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但没人提起过\N{\rENG}But no one said anything
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}前方需要面对的拒绝与忧伤\N{\rENG}about all the rejection and sadness there was to be found.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}日复一日的试镜\N{\rENG}So many auditions day after day.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}日复一日的被拒\N{\rENG}So much rejection day after day.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是为什么我回来了\N{\rENG}That's why I came back.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}再有一个拒绝就会摧毁我幼小的内心\N{\rENG}One more rejection would have destroyed my fragile heart.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起\N{\rENG}Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有时我会不由自主的深沉装B, 你清楚吗? \N{\rENG}Sometimes, I get caught up in the drama zone, you know?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错, 深沉装B\N{\rENG}Yeah, right. Drama zone.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 既然这样, 我有个消息要给你--\N{\rENG}Oh, by the way, we have something for y--
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不, 我们没有! \N{\rENG}no, we don't!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们怎么能在现在把这封信给杰米呢? \N{\rENG}How can we give this letter to Jamie now?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他很可能会伤心的\N{\rENG}He might get upset.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能做点调整\N{\rENG}We can make adjustments.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们可以调整为杰米的诗意语言\N{\rENG}We can match Jamie's poetic language
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让他轻松的接受\N{\rENG}and let him down easy.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我看过几集烂俗的肥皂剧\N{\rENG}I watched some episodes of a torrid soap opera once,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.02,0:06:09.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我很自信能把握住浪漫的要领\N{\rENG}so I'm confident that I get the gist of romance.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看! \N{\rENG}There!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.08,0:06:12.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} "亲爱的杰米...\N{\rENG}"Dear Jamie...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你, 亲爱的山茶花, \N{\rENG}You, dear camellia,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}心怀期待的等待我如明月般的光亮, \N{\rENG}expectantly await the light of my moon,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我的光亮更似炙烤, \N{\rENG}yet my light is more of a scorching,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让你枯萎, 如同沙漠热浪\N{\rENG}wilting, dry desert heat.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而作为你比喻上的手术师\N{\rENG}And as your metaphorical surgeon,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.68,0:06:24.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我怀着沉重的内心\N{\rENG}it is with a heavy heart
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}敦促你寻找其他的人选\N{\rENG}that I urge you to seek a second opinion.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我将心返还给你" --\N{\rENG}I return your heart to you" --
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} "同时, 你头发很漂亮" \N{\rENG}"also, your hair is nice."
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} "头发...很...\N{\rENG}"Hair...Is...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}漂亮\N{\rENG}Nice.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的, 但不属于你, 石榴" \N{\rENG}Yours, but not really, Garnet."
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.24,0:06:38.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}完美\N{\rENG}Perfect.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}任务完成\N{\rENG}Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴! \N{\rENG}Garnet!
Dialogue: 600,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.58,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处背景音乐源自 "动物之森" 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.60,0:06:50.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴! \N{\rENG}Garnet!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}汝何在, 我甜蜜, 炙烤的阳光? \N{\rENG}Where art thou, my sweet scorching sunbeam?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 不! \N{\rENG}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.96,0:06:56.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴! \N{\rENG}Garnet!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我阅读了汝信, 而我理解了! \N{\rENG}I read thine letter, and I understand!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}汝返还吾心! \N{\rENG}Thou hast return eth mine heart!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊?! 不, 那不是--\N{\rENG}What?! No, that's not what --
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.68,0:07:08.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴, 你喜欢着我的头发, 如我爱慕你的一样\N{\rENG}Garnet, you like my hair just as I adore yours.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来到我的怀抱中吧, 石榴\N{\rENG}Come to me, Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米! \N{\rENG}Jamie!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊, 少主史蒂文! \N{\rENG}Ah, young master Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.96,0:07:15.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}赞美汝, 石榴女士何在? \N{\rENG}Pray thee, where is lady Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.62,0:07:16.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她...\N{\rENG}She...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她不--她不会来了\N{\rENG}She's n-- she's not coming.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我专门来此表明我对我的女人的爱意! \N{\rENG}But I've come to proclaim my love for my woman!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不, 杰米, 你不了解! 我--\N{\rENG}No, Jamie, you don't understand! I --
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴! 你来了! \N{\rENG}Garnet! You've come!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你可以告诉史蒂文所有的\N{\rENG}You can tell Steven about all the beautiful things
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你写给我的信件中的华丽辞藻\N{\rENG}you wrote to me in your missive.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可不是那么写的\N{\rENG}I didn't write that.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但就在这里啊! \N{\rENG}But it's all right here!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.48,0:07:39.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}沾上了喜悦的泪水--现在还有雨水\N{\rENG}Stained with tears of joy -- and now also rain.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是康妮和我写的, 杰米! \N{\rENG}Connie and I wrote that letter, Jamie!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈? \N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很抱歉, 杰米\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry, Jamie.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们只是想让你不要太伤心\N{\rENG}We just wanted to let you down easy.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}汝不愿炙烤吾, 吾之爱日? \N{\rENG}Wilst thou not scorch me, my darling sun?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.56,0:07:55.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不会, 以后也不会, 有兴趣\N{\rENG}I am not, nor will I ever be, interested.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}gun滚! \N{\rENG}Go away!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我的小心脏啊! \N{\rENG}M-my panache!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰～米～! \N{\rENG}Jamieeeee!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 天哪\N{\rENG}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我真为可怜的杰米感到伤心\N{\rENG}I feel so bad for poor Jamie.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.48,0:08:17.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错, 但我确定他立刻就能走出这一切\N{\rENG}Yeah. But I'm sure he'll bounce back from this in no time.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他随时都可能带着信件出现\N{\rENG}He's probably gonna show up with the mail any moment now.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.41,0:08:21.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打扰一下, 小子们\N{\rENG}Excuse me, kids.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在寻找...\N{\rENG}I'm looking for the home of...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文·宇宙的家? \N{\rENG}Steven Universe?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就是史蒂文·宇宙的家\N{\rENG}I'm the home of Steven Universe.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿, 你是格雷格的孩子\N{\rENG}Hey, you're Greg's boy.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为杰米在开玩笑\N{\rENG}I thought Jamie was pulling my leg
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他之前说你就住在这里\N{\rENG}when he told me you were living over here.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等, 那杰米呢? \N{\rENG}W-wait. Where is Jamie?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.32,0:08:40.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊, 那个可怜的孩子完全崩溃了\N{\rENG}Aw, that poor kid's emotions have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?! \N{\rENG}What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错, 他简直一团糟! \N{\rENG}Yeah, he's a mess!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他说自己无法承受再次往这里送邮件了\N{\rENG}Said he couldn't bear to deliver mail on this route again
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}自从他被拒绝后\N{\rENG}after having his love spurned.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他这么说的\N{\rENG}He said it just like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像--就像, 当他深沉的装B时\N{\rENG}Like -- like, when he's in the drama zone.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.04,0:08:54.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}接着他握紧了自己的拳头, 闭上了眼睛, 像这样\N{\rENG}Then he clenched his fist and closed his eyes like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真是装B一绝啊\N{\rENG}Full of drama to the end.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不管怎样, 这里是一本折扣券\N{\rENG}Anyway, here's a book of coupons.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.38,0:08:59.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}祝好! \N{\rENG}Have a good one!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看起来很伤心\N{\rENG}You look sad.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们这次真的搞砸了\N{\rENG}We really messed up this time.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.08,0:09:18.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为我们, 杰米前所未有的低沉\N{\rENG}Because of us, Jamie's feeling lower than ever.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们粉碎了他的意志! \N{\rENG}We've shattered the man!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他不会再爱了\N{\rENG}He'll never love again!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.88,0:09:23.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会跟他谈谈的\N{\rENG}I'll go talk to him.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你的言语会摧毁他的! \N{\rENG}But your words will destroy him!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能不能, 像是, 擦除他的大脑\N{\rENG}Can't you just, like, zap his brain
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后他就不会记得这一切? \N{\rENG}so he forgets any of this ever happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米\N{\rENG}Jamie.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴\N{\rENG}Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不是要伤你的心\N{\rENG}I didn't mean to upset you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么你愿意和我约吗? \N{\rENG}Then will you go out with me?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.68,0:09:48.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! \N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我自从看到你的那一刻就爱上你的\N{\rENG}But I've loved you since the moment I saw you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一见钟情并不存在\N{\rENG}Love at first sight doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.14,0:09:56.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}爱需要时间, 还有精力\N{\rENG}Love takes time, and love takes work.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}再怎么说, 至少你也得了解另一半\N{\rENG}At the very least, you have to know the other person.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.76,0:10:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而你真的不清楚我到底是什么\N{\rENG}And you literally have no idea who or what I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.66,0:10:09.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我为你盛开了, 就像--就像月光下的山茶花\N{\rENG}But I bloom for you, like -- like a camellia under moonlight.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不, 你没有! \N{\rENG}No, you don't!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你假扮了一个热恋中的蠢蛋\N{\rENG}You make a very convincing lovesick fool.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你骗到了这两个孩子\N{\rENG}You convinced these children.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你甚至骗了自己\N{\rENG}You even convinced yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是个非常好的演员\N{\rENG}You're a fantastic actor.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那我现在该做什么? \N{\rENG}What am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}从本地剧院开始\N{\rENG}Start with local theater.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.38,0:10:30.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还好吗? \N{\rENG}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.98,0:10:31.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没事\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那些建议含金量很高\N{\rENG}That was some pretty solid advice.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那些是你写给石榴的信吗? \N{\rENG}Were those more letters you wrote to Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不, 那些只是邮件\N{\rENG}No, that was the mail
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我本该将这些信件送达的\N{\rENG}I was supposed to deliver on my last route.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们会帮你收集的\N{\rENG}We'll help you pick it all up.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢\N{\rENG}Thanks.
